title: Brutal Honesty and The Oscars
description:
LaLa and Randall are flying solo with stories about Randall's Oscar night experience, and LaLa's take on Vanderpump Rules and the new cast. It's brutal honesty capped with some fun answers to your voicemail questions! Who would La & Rand cast to play themselves in a movie? And how did Rand handle all the drama with Vanderpump Rules' James Kennedy?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
